1>Decorator Design Pattern

    Used when we need to add additional features on one object and then the new object
    created uspe bhi hum naye feature add on kar skahte hai

Use Case
    1>Pizza Shop
        Base Pizza
        Toppings
            ExtraCheese
            Mushroom
            Jalepeno
        ExtraVeggies
            Toamto
            Onion
            Brocolli
    2>Coffee
        Base COfee
            DEcaf
            Cappciono
        Cream
        Milk
        SoyaMilk
    3>Car
        Base Car
        SeatCover
        FogLight
        Ac
        PowerSteering

Why we need decorator pattern
    To avoid ClassExplosion
    Jaise ab car me case me agar decotatpr pattern follow nahi karte to kitini car banuga mai
    BaseCar + Ac ki ek class
    Base Car + Ac+ Power Steering ki ek etc etc
    And this way we will explosde our numebr of class for all possible permutation and combination
